<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">١ ـ بَاءُ الاِسْتِعَانَة:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">بِاسْمِ الله:</span> الْبَاء لِلاِسْتِعَانَةُ وَإِظْهَارُ الحَاجَةِ وَتَقْدِيرُهُ: أَسْتَعِينُ بِالله ٠<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">٢ ـ بَاءُ السَّبَبِيَّة:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>بَلْ لاَ بُدَّ مِنَ الْعَمَل؛<span class="c5"> أَلَمْ تَسْمَعْ إِلىَ قَوْلِهِ جَلَّ وَعَلاَ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
